'''Hrru''' iga yan wassaɣ amaziɣ n tmɣart. yan ɣ ussaɣ iqburn lli sul illan tisgiwin n idrarn n [[Adrar n drn|Atlas]] d [[Sus|tasga n Sus]] dar [[Idawtanan]]. Mac ussaɣn ad lli ugan sul fllas zzyyar ɣ tmura n [[Tamzɣa|tafrikt n ugaffa]] niɣd [[tamzɣa]]. Afagan [[amaziɣ]] ifl ɣ gigan d isrfan ns. tlkm fllas tizi lliɣ fllas illa ad iddr tawsna ns yiligsn asrf ns f masa ism arraw ns s ussaɣn imaziɣn.
Ar nttafa ussaɣ ad tar ya tamdyast tamqrant Herru n Ssi Ḥmmu lli ittuyssan s timdyazin ns lli ikkatn simẓint agllid Hassan amzwaru.
